===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], Promise City had a population of 88, with 35 households and 20 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A64875&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A64875&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A64875&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

The [[population density]] was 477.0 inhabitants per square mile (184.2/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 54 housing units at an average density of 292.7 per square mile (113.0/km<sup>2</sup>), of which 35.2% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 9.1% and the rental vacancy rate was 37.5%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

Of the 35 households, 25.7% had children under the age of 18 living in them. Of all households, 37.1% were married-couple households, 8.6% were cohabitating couple households, 34.3% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present, and 20.0% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present. 42.9% of households were non-families. About 37.1% of all households were made up of individuals, and 25.7% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age in the city was 40.0 years. 26.1% of residents were under the age of 18 and 22.7% were 65 years of age or older. By broader age groups, 27.3% of residents were under the age of 20; 4.5% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 20.5% were from 25 to 44; and 25.0% were from 45 to 64. The gender makeup of the city was 48.9% male and 51.1% female. For every 100 females there were 95.6 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 109.7 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

